trustdetails.trustname: Reg MIS trust with ten directors

nominationSectionDescription.string: You are required under the Anti-Money Laundering and Counter-Terrorism Financing Act 2006 to identify anyone who directly or indirectly owns 25% or more of the company acting as trustee. Ensure you also record the details of anyone who is a beneficiary of the trust.

shareholderandmembers.additionalPersonSectionDescription: Add any additional beneficiaries of the trust or shareholders of the trustee company with a 25% or more share ownership.
